      <data key="d16">["Home, bedroom"]</data>
      <data key="d17">[{"Time": "2025-01-03 07:00:00", "Location": "Home, bedroom", "Audio": "Speaker 1: Alright kids, time to get up, um, you know, school's not gonna wait for us, so basically, let's get moving.Speaker 2: Okay so, sweetie, remember when we talked about getting dressed quickly, how about you guys get started on that.Speaker 3: But why do I have to wear a uniform, actually, I know that it's the rule, but can I wear my favorite shirt instead.Speaker 1: Um, no, you know, the thing is, uniforms are, uh, required, so just put it on, okay.Speaker 4: Mommy look, I made a snowflake, can I show it to daddy.Speaker 2: That's nice sweetie, but first, let's get you dressed, and then you can show it to daddy.Speaker 5: Me too, me too, I want to show daddy something, look look.Speaker 1: Okay, buddy, what do you want to show me, uh, so basically, let me see.Speaker 3: I know that we have to leave early today, but can I finish my book, please.Speaker 2: Okay, sweetie, but just for a few minutes, we don't want to be late, so basically, let's hurry up.Speaker 4: I want pancakes, mommy, please please, can I have pancakes.Speaker 2: Okay, sweetie, we can make some pancakes, but just a few, because we need to get going soon.Speaker 1: Um, so, you know, I was thinking, maybe we can, uh, make some scrambled eggs too, so basically, let's do that.Speaker 5: No, no, I don't want eggs, I want cereal, why do we have to have eggs.Speaker 3: Actually, eggs are good for you, because they have protein, and stuff.Speaker 2: That's right, sweetie, eggs are a good choice, but you can have cereal if you want, how about that.Speaker 4: That's not fair, I want cereal too, mommy look, I'm making a face.Speaker 1: Okay, okay, so, you know, let's just, uh, calm down, and have a good breakfast, okay.Speaker 5: Look look, I made a mess, oh no, sorry daddy.Speaker 2: It's okay, sweetie, accidents happen, let's just clean it up, and move on.Speaker 3: Can I help with the cleaning, because I know that we need to, you know, work together.Speaker 1: Um, yeah, that's a great idea, so basically, let's all pitch in, and get it done.Speaker 4: I want to help too, mommy, please please, can I use the sponge.Speaker 2: Okay, sweetie, but be careful, because we don't want any more messes, so basically, just use it gently.Speaker 5: Me too, me too, I want to use the sponge, why can't I.Speaker 1: Okay, buddy, you can help, but just, uh, hold the sponge, and let your sister do the cleaning, okay.Speaker 3: Actually, I think we should, you know, make a schedule, so we can, uh, get everything done on time.Speaker 2: That's a great idea, sweetie, let's make a schedule, and stick to it, so basically, let's do that.Speaker 4: Mommy look, I'm finished cleaning, can I have a pancake now.Speaker 2: Okay, sweetie, you can have a pancake, but just one, because we need to, you know, get going soon.Speaker 1: Um, so, you know, I was thinking, maybe we can, uh, listen to some music, on the way to school, so basically, let's do that.Speaker 5: Yeah, yeah, I want to listen to music, look look, I'm dancing.Speaker 3: Actually, I think we should, you know, study for our tests, instead of listening to music, because we need to, uh, focus.Speaker 2: That's a good idea, sweetie, but we can, uh, listen to music, and still study, so basically, let's do both.Speaker 4: I don't want to study, I want to play, mommy, please please.Speaker 1: Okay, okay, so, you know, let's just, uh, calm down, and get ready, okay, we're running late.", "Image": "A bedroom with beige carpet flooring and cream-colored walls. A modern, dark brown wooden bed frame with a white duvet and a few stuffed animals on it is visible, along with a white dresser with a flat-screen TV on top and a few school backpacks and lunchboxes on the floor nearby. A window with frosty glass and light snow outside lets in soft, natural light, illuminating the room."}]</data>
      <data key="d18">["A bedroom with beige carpet flooring and cream-colored walls. A modern, dark brown wooden bed frame with a white duvet and a few stuffed animals on it is visible, along with a white dresser with a flat-screen TV on top and a few school backpacks and lunchboxes on the floor nearby. A window with frosty glass and light snow outside lets in soft, natural light, illuminating the room."]</data>
      <data key="d19">A bedroom with beige carpet flooring and cream-colored walls. A modern, dark brown wooden bed frame with a white duvet and a few stuffed animals on it is visible, along with a white dresser with a flat-screen TV on top and a few school backpacks and lunchboxes on the floor nearby. A window with frosty glass and light snow outside lets in soft, natural light, illuminating the room.</data>
