      <data key="d0">CHUNK</data>
      <data key="d1">lexical_graph</data>
      <data key="d20">so, um, let's just focus, okay?Speaker 2: Sweetie, don't forget your backpack, you have a lot of homework to do tonight.Speaker 4: I want to do my homework now, mommy, can I?Speaker 5: Me too, me too, I want to do homework, why can't I?Speaker 1: Um, so, not right now, kids, we need to, uh, get to school first, and, you know, then you can do your homework.Speaker 2: Okay, so, let's get going, kids, we don't want to be late.Speaker 3: Actually, I'm ready, can we go now?Speaker 4: Mommy, look, I'm ready, see?Speaker 1: So, uh, let's go, kids, we're all set, and, um, have a great day at school, okay?</data>
