      <data key="d16">["Office, 23rd floor conference room"]</data>
      <data key="d17">[{"Time": "2025-01-03 11:36:00", "Location": "Office, 23rd floor conference room", "Audio": "Speaker 1: So basically, I was thinking, um, we should probably get the kids' school stuff organized for next semester, you know?Speaker 2: Okay so, I was looking at the calendar and I think we have a parent-teacher conference coming up, sweetie, remember when we had to do that last year?Speaker 1: The thing is, I'm not sure if I can make it, I have a meeting at work that I really need to be at, um, it's about this new project we're starting.Speaker 2: How about I go to the conference and you can, you know, catch up with the teacher later, maybe over email or something?Speaker 3: Mommy, Mommy, can I have a snack?Speaker 2: Sweetie, not right now, we're in a meeting, okay?Speaker 1: So, uh, what were we talking about again?Speaker 2: The parent-teacher conference, and I was saying maybe I can go and you can follow up with the teacher later.Speaker 3: But I'm hungry, Mommy, I want goldfish crackers!Speaker 2: Okay, sweetie, just a minute, Mommy's busy right now.Speaker 1: You know, I was thinking, um, maybe we can, like, prep some meals for the week, you know, to make mornings easier?Speaker 2: That's a great idea, sweetie, how about we make some, uh, pasta salad or something?Speaker 4: Look, Daddy, I made a castle with my blocks!Speaker 1: That's, uh, really cool, buddy, I'll take a look in a minute, okay?Speaker 2: Okay so, what time is your meeting at work, do you know yet?Speaker 1: Um, let me check, I think it's at, like, 2 o'clock or something.Speaker 3: Mommy, can I play with my toys now?Speaker 2: Yes, sweetie, you can play, just be quiet for a minute, okay?Speaker 1: So, basically, I think we need to, you know, finalize the plans for the Smith account, and, uh, get the report done by Friday.Speaker 2: Okay, got it, I'll make sure to, you know, remind you about it later, sweetie.Speaker 4: Daddy, Daddy, I want to show you something!Speaker 1: What is it, buddy, what do you want to show me?Speaker 3: Mommy, I don't like goldfish crackers, I want animal crackers!Speaker 2: Sweetie, we just got the goldfish crackers, how about we finish those first, okay?Speaker 1: You know, I was thinking, um, maybe we can, like, take the kids to the park this weekend, if the weather's not too cold.Speaker 2: That sounds like a great idea, sweetie, how about we, uh, check the weather forecast later and see what it says?Speaker 4: I want to go to the park, yeah!Speaker 3: Me too, me too, I want to go on the swings!Speaker 1: So, basically, I think we're, uh, good for now, unless anyone has anything else to add?Speaker 2: Okay so, just to recap, we need to, you know, get the kids' school stuff organized, and, uh, prep some meals for the week, right?Speaker 1: That's right, and, um, I'll try to, you know, catch up with the teacher later, okay?Speaker 2: Sounds good, sweetie, I'll, uh, send you a reminder about it later.Speaker 3: Mommy, I'm bored, can I watch TV now?Speaker 2: Not right now, sweetie, we're almost done with the meeting, okay?Speaker 1: You know, I was thinking, um, maybe we can, like, have a family dinner night this week, and, uh, make some, you know, healthy food or something.Speaker 2: That's a great idea, sweetie, how about we, uh, plan it for, like, Wednesday or something?Speaker 4: Yay, family dinner night, yeah!", "Image": "A conference room with dark gray carpeted flooring and beige walls. A large, rectangular wooden table with a glossy finish dominates the center of the room, surrounded by high-backed, black leather office chairs. The table holds a stainless steel water pitcher, several empty glasses, and a few open laptops with silver bodies and black keyboards."}]</data>
      <data key="d18">["A conference room with dark gray carpeted flooring and beige walls. A large, rectangular wooden table with a glossy finish dominates the center of the room, surrounded by high-backed, black leather office chairs. The table holds a stainless steel water pitcher, several empty glasses, and a few open laptops with silver bodies and black keyboards."]</data>
      <data key="d19">A conference room with dark gray carpeted flooring and beige walls. A large, rectangular wooden table with a glossy finish dominates the center of the room, surrounded by high-backed, black leather office chairs. The table holds a stainless steel water pitcher, several empty glasses, and a few open laptops with silver bodies and black keyboards.</data>
