      <data key="d17">[{"Time": "2025-01-03 14:12:00", "Location": "Office, cafeteria", "Audio": "Speaker 1: So I was thinking, you know, we should probably get the kids to eat something before we head out, um, to their piano lessons, the thing is, they've been starving all morningSpeaker 2: Daddy, I wanna get a cookie, can I get a cookie?Speaker 1: Uh, well, let's see, so basically, we need to get you guys to eat something healthy first, like, you know, a sandwich or somethingSpeaker 3: But why, I don't wanna eat a sandwich, I hate sandwichesSpeaker 2: Yeah, I hate sandwiches too, can we get pizza?Speaker 1: Um, no, not pizza, so, the thing is, we just had pizza for dinner last night, you know?Speaker 4: Look, Daddy, a bird outside, can we feed it?Speaker 1: Uh, no, not right now, so, we need to focus on getting you guys to eat something, like, you know, some fruit or somethingSpeaker 2: I wanna eat a cookie, pleeease?Speaker 3: Yeah, me too, I wanna eat a cookieSpeaker 1: Okay, fine, so, one cookie each, but just one, you know?Speaker 4: Yay, thank you, Daddy, can we get hot chocolate too?Speaker 1: Um, well, let's see, so basically, we need to get going soon, but, uh, yeah, sure, you can get hot chocolateSpeaker 2: I wanna put whipped cream on my hot chocolate, can I?Speaker 3: Yeah, me too, I wanna put whipped cream on mineSpeaker 1: So, okay, sure, you can both get whipped cream, the thing is, we just need to, you know, hurry up a bitSpeaker 4: Daddy, my cookie is too crunchy, can I get a softer one?Speaker 1: Uh, well, let me see, so, we can try to, you know, find a softer one for youSpeaker 2: I like my cookie, it's so yummySpeaker 3: Yeah, me too, I love cookiesSpeaker 1: Okay, good, so, now that we have our snacks, we should, uh, get going, you know?Speaker 4: But, Daddy, I don't wanna go, I wanna play with the toys hereSpeaker 1: Um, well, so, the thing is, we need to get you guys to your piano lessons, it's, you know, importantSpeaker 2: Yeah, and then we can come back and play, right?Speaker 3: Yeah, right, Daddy, you promisedSpeaker 1: So, okay, let's get going, and, uh, we'll come back and play later, you know?Speaker 4: Can we get ice cream after piano lessons, pleeease?Speaker 1: Uh, well, let's see, so, we'll, you know, talk about it later, okay?Speaker 2: I wanna tell Mommy about my piano lesson, can I call her?Speaker 3: Yeah, me too, I wanna tell Mommy about my lessonSpeaker 1: So, okay, sure, you can both call Mommy later, the thing is, we need to, you know, focus on getting to the lessons right nowSpeaker 4: Daddy, I'm cold, can I wear my jacket?Speaker 1: Um, well, yeah, sure, you can wear your jacket, it's, you know, pretty cold outsideSpeaker 2: I'm cold too, can I wear my jacket too?Speaker 3: Yeah, me too, I'm coldSpeaker 1: So, okay, everyone get your jackets, and, uh, let's get going, you know?", "Image": "A counter with a stainless steel coffee machine and a stack of white ceramic cups sits beneath fluorescent lighting. The floor is made of dark gray speckled linoleum and the walls are painted a pale yellow color. A row of modern-style chairs with silver frames and black seats are arranged along a nearby table with a few abandoned lunch trays and a discarded newspaper."}]</data>
      <data key="d18">["A counter with a stainless steel coffee machine and a stack of white ceramic cups sits beneath fluorescent lighting. The floor is made of dark gray speckled linoleum and the walls are painted a pale yellow color. A row of modern-style chairs with silver frames and black seats are arranged along a nearby table with a few abandoned lunch trays and a discarded newspaper."]</data>
      <data key="d19">A counter with a stainless steel coffee machine and a stack of white ceramic cups sits beneath fluorescent lighting. The floor is made of dark gray speckled linoleum and the walls are painted a pale yellow color. A row of modern-style chairs with silver frames and black seats are arranged along a nearby table with a few abandoned lunch trays and a discarded newspaper.</data>
