      <data key="d0">CHUNK</data>
      <data key="d1">lexical_graph</data>
      <data key="d20">you can get hot chocolateSpeaker 2: I wanna put whipped cream on my hot chocolate, can I?Speaker 3: Yeah, me too, I wanna put whipped cream on mineSpeaker 1: So, okay, sure, you can both get whipped cream, the thing is, we just need to, you know, hurry up a bitSpeaker 4: Daddy, my cookie is too crunchy, can I get a softer one?Speaker 1: Uh, well, let me see, so, we can try to, you know, find a softer one for youSpeaker 2: I like my cookie, it's so yummySpeaker 3: Yeah, me too, I love cookiesSpeaker 1: Okay, good, so, now that we have our snacks, we should, uh, get going, you know?Speaker 4: But, Daddy, I don't wanna go, I wanna play with the toys hereSpeaker 1: Um, well, so, the thing is, we need to get you guys to your piano lessons, it's, you know, importantSpeaker 2: Yeah, and then we can come back and play, right?Speaker 3: Yeah, right, Daddy, you promisedSpeaker 1: So, okay, let's get going, and, uh, we'll come back and play later, you know?Speaker 4: Can we get ice cream after piano lessons, pleeease?Speaker 1: Uh, well, let's see, so, we'll, you know, talk about it later, okay?Speaker 2: I wanna tell Mommy about my piano lesson, can I call her?Speaker 3: Yeah, me too, I</data>
