      <data key="d0">CHUNK</data>
      <data key="d1">lexical_graph</data>
      <data key="d20">okay?Speaker 2: I wanna tell Mommy about my piano lesson, can I call her?Speaker 3: Yeah, me too, I wanna tell Mommy about my lessonSpeaker 1: So, okay, sure, you can both call Mommy later, the thing is, we need to, you know, focus on getting to the lessons right nowSpeaker 4: Daddy, I'm cold, can I wear my jacket?Speaker 1: Um, well, yeah, sure, you can wear your jacket, it's, you know, pretty cold outsideSpeaker 2: I'm cold too, can I wear my jacket too?Speaker 3: Yeah, me too, I'm coldSpeaker 1: So, okay, everyone get your jackets, and, uh, let's get going, you know?</data>
