    <node id="SEGMENT_2025-01-03_EPISODE_007_CHUNK_0_0">
      <data key="d0">CHUNK</data>
      <data key="d1">lexical_graph</data>
      <data key="d20">Speaker 1: So basically, I had a meeting at work today, and, uh, it was pretty long, you know, we were discussing this new project, and, um, I think it's gonna be a big deal, but, so, I'm not really sure how it's gonna affect my schedule, yet.Speaker 2: Okay, so, how was your day, sweetie, I mean, aside from the meeting, did you, uh, get a chance to, you know, grab some lunch?Speaker 3: Daddy, Daddy, I'm hungry, can we get some dumplings when we get home?Speaker 1: Um, yeah, sure thing, kiddo, we'll, uh, see what Mom says, okay?Speaker 2: How about we make some noodles instead, sweetie, we have some vegetables at home that need to be used up, remember when we went to the market last weekend?Speaker 4: Mommy, Mommy, look at this! I drew a picture of our cat, Mr. Whiskers!Speaker 2: Oh, that's so cute, sweetie, let me see, um, what's Mr. Whiskers doing in the picture?Speaker 1: So, anyway, like I was saying, this project at work, it's, uh, gonna be a challenge, but, you know, I think we can handle it, the thing is, we need to, um, work together as a team.Speaker 3: Daddy, can I play with my toy car when we get home, pleeease?Speaker 2: Okay, sweetie, but first, let's get some dinner,</data>
