      <data key="d17">[{"Time": "2025-01-03 21:36:00", "Location": "Home, living room", "Audio": "Speaker 1: Okay, so, um, let's get the kids ready for bed, you know, it's already pretty lateSpeaker 2: Sweetie, I think we should, okay so, have them brush their teeth first, and then we can read a bookSpeaker 3: But why do I have to go to bed so early, I'm not tired, actually, I was just reading this really cool bookSpeaker 4: Mommy look, I made a picture, can I show it to you, please pleaseSpeaker 1: Uh, yeah, sure thing, sweetie, let me just, you know, finish talking to mom for a secondSpeaker 2: Remember when we used to have to wake them up early for school, now they just want to stay up all nightSpeaker 5: Me too, me too, I want to stay up, why do I have to go to bedSpeaker 3: Because you're little, and you need to sleep, so your body can grow strongSpeaker 4: That's not fair, I'm big too, I can stay up, look look, I can touch the ceilingSpeaker 1: So, uh, what's for breakfast tomorrow, did we decide on, um, pancakes or wafflesSpeaker 2: Oh, I think we said pancakes, but we need to get some more syrup, I don't think we have enoughSpeaker 5: I want syrup, I love syrup, can I have some nowSpeaker 3: No, you can't have syrup now, it's too close to bedtime, and it's not good for youSpeaker 4: Mommy, can I have a glass of water, I'm thirstySpeaker 2: Okay, sweetie, I'll get you a glass of water, but then you need to get ready for bedSpeaker 1: So, um, I was thinking, you know, we should, uh, start getting them to pack their own lunches, it's time they learnedSpeaker 3: But why do I have to pack my own lunch, can't you just do it for meSpeaker 5: I want to pack my lunch, I can do it, look look, I can make a sandwichSpeaker 2: That's a great idea, sweetie, you can help us pack your lunch, and learn how to make a sandwichSpeaker 4: Mommy look, my toothbrush is pink, and my brother's is blueSpeaker 1: Uh, yeah, that's right, sweetie, you have a pink toothbrush, and your brother has a blue oneSpeaker 3: Actually, I know that, can I go brush my teeth nowSpeaker 2: Okay, sweetie, go brush your teeth, and then we'll read a bookSpeaker 5: I want to brush my teeth too, me tooSpeaker 1: So, um, I was thinking, you know, we should, uh, start a, uh, schedule for the kids, so they know what to expectSpeaker 2: That's a great idea, sweetie, we can make a schedule, and post it on the fridgeSpeaker 3: But why do we need a schedule, can't we just, you know, do things when we wantSpeaker 4: Mommy, can I have a story, please please, I want to hear a storySpeaker 1: Uh, yeah, sure thing, sweetie, we'll read a story, but then it's time for bedSpeaker 2: Okay, sweetie, let's get ready for bed, and then we'll read a storySpeaker 5: I'm tired, I want to sleep, look look, I'm sleepySpeaker 3: Actually, I'm not tired, can I stay up and read some moreSpeaker 1: So, uh, no, you can't stay up, it's time for bed, you need to get some sleepSpeaker 2: Sweetie, it's time for bed, let's go get ready, and then we'll read a storySpeaker 4: Mommy look, I'm ready for bed, I have my favorite toySpeaker 1: Uh, yeah, great, sweetie, let's get you to bed, and then we can, uh, relax for a bitSpeaker 2: Okay, sweetie, let's get you to bed, and then we can, okay so, watch a movie or somethingSpeaker 3: But why can't I watch a movie, it's not fairSpeaker 5: Me too, me too, I want to watch a movieSpeaker 1: So, um, we'll see, you know, maybe tomorrow, we can watch a movie, but for now, it's time for bedSpeaker 2: Okay, sweetie, let's get you to bed, and then we can, uh, talk about it in the morningSpeaker 4: Mommy, I love you, goodnightSpeaker 1: Uh, yeah, I love you too, sweetie, goodnightSpeaker 3: Goodnight, I'll see you in the morningSpeaker 5: Night night, I'm sleepy", "Image": "A room with dark gray carpeting and beige walls, illuminated by a table lamp with a white shade on a wooden side table. A brown leather sofa is visible in the background, with a few stuffed animals and a throw blanket in a vibrant purple color scattered on it. A TV stand with a large flat-screen TV sits against one wall, with a few framed family photos on the shelves below."}]</data>
      <data key="d18">["A room with dark gray carpeting and beige walls, illuminated by a table lamp with a white shade on a wooden side table. A brown leather sofa is visible in the background, with a few stuffed animals and a throw blanket in a vibrant purple color scattered on it. A TV stand with a large flat-screen TV sits against one wall, with a few framed family photos on the shelves below."]</data>
